  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Woodpeckers are the kind of creature that after being offended not only sulk for months, but demands official apologies in writing, countersigned by at least two witnesses, a gift of reconciliation and a visit to the offender’s own (often remote) home in order to look the culprit of the affront in the eye while being apologized to. They are stubborn, touchy, easily irritated and undoubtedly the least social of all Pici. Nonetheless, they are not cold hearted, even if they try not to show it. If a loved one suffers or needs support, they secretly work to get them what they need, large or small. Industrious, savers and moderate, however, they are capable of great gestures of kindness, which is given in the strictest confidence, and they are very sensitive to injustices, to which they react more with deeds than with words. Unique among the Pici, they do not possess the gift of singing, which they silently admire: music is their weak point, and the only thing that generates genuine emotion in them.</span> <br style=\"font-variant-numeric:normal;font-variant-east-asian:normal;line-height:normal;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-size-adjust:auto\" /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Increase in Ability Scores.</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Dexterity </span>score increases by 2 and your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Constitution </span>score increases by 1.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Age.</strong></em> </span>A Pici reaches maturity around the age of 14 <span class=\"fontstyle0\">and is immediately considered independent. They have an average lifespan of around 60 years.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Speed. </strong></em></span></span>Your base speed on the ground is 20 feet, and your <span class=\"fontstyle0\">flight speed is 30 feet.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Size. </strong></em></span>A Woodpecker can reach a maximum height of 3 <span class=\"fontstyle0\">feet, and weigh no more than 65 lbs.</span>  <span class=\"fontstyle2\">Your size is  <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Small</span>.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.ZLta2Wjm3OsgNAk0]{Wings}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.9ALHHLuQoSWQRqN4]{Prehensile Legs}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.avDL8Y6OdU8uPhkn]{Stubborn}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.3IW3nTEcERwHG4Qg]{Agile}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.ZQMtMEJZdQJ2v63O]{Social Skills}<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.K3vkJOhbY84KuNmD]{Maneuvers in Flight}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.2zVRhhfSO8fMZWzt]{Acute Sight}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.species-features.ZKtY9GrvhkuMK0mv]{Peck}</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><em><strong>Instinct of Familia, Harmless (Prey):</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle4\">“I am often not taken seriously.”</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><em><strong>Instinct of Species, Solitary:</strong></em> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">“I can be alone and keep others at a distance”.</span></p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
